; Coverage for amount.cc
; Multiplying an amount by a percentage divides by 100 internally.
; $100 * 19% = $19.00 (the "%" commodity triggers the special
; division-by-100 logic). The result keeps the original commodity ($).

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(amount * 19%)\n"
$19.00
$-19.00
end test
